2F%2Fcouncilonstrategicrisks.org%2F2023%2F08%2F01%2Fending-tactical-nuclear-weapons%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edesigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%201950s%20in%20order%20to%20dissuade%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20from%20attacking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20twin-mount%2038-caliber%20gun%20turret%20was%20once%20used%20to%20shoot%20down%20planes%20on%20the%20USS%20Reno.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20weapon%20on%20display%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666cb7b7ed9a404d829e1b37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20weapon%20on%20display%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDecommissioned%20in%201946%2C%20the%20USS%20Reno%20earned%20three%20battle%20stars%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Navy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20plenty%20to%20see%2C%20but%20much%20of%20the%20space%20remains%20under%20construction%20until%20the%20museum's%20new%20permanent%20home%20is%20ready.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20exhibit%20under%20construction%20at%20the%20National%20Museum%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Navy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666ca9be764df161125a28bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20exhibit%20under%20construction.%3Cp%3ETalia%20Lakritz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20items%20on%20display%20didn't%20have%20accompanying%20plaques%20explaining%20their%20historical%20significance.%20During%20my%20first%20lap%20around%20the%20museum%2C%20I%20walked%20right%20past%20the%20nuclear-weapon%20exhibits%20without%20knowing%20what%20they%20were.%20I%20found%20that