3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20ways%20to%20diversify%20your%20income.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOnce%20you%20have%20a%20spending%20strategy%20in%20place%2C%20Truong%20recommends%20exploring%20ways%20to%20increase%20wealth%20and%20diversify%20your%20income%20sources%20%E2%80%94%20for%20instance%2C%20through%20your%20job%2C%20benefits%2C%20side%20gigs%2C%20and%20investments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EDon't%20let%20emotions%20drive%20your%20decisions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20help%20your%20family%20learn%20to%20do%20the%20same%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmotions%20are%20normal%2C%20but%20don't%20let%20them%20drive%20your%20money%20decisions%2C%20recommends%20Truong.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20respond%20to%20the%20emotions%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20react%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BStep%20back%20and%20ask%20yourself%20why%20you%20feel%20this%20way.%20Do%20you%20think%20these%20feelings%20are%20reflecting%20your%20current%20situation%20correctly%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20want%20to%20steer%20your%20family%20toward%20financial%20education%20and%20resources%20%E2%80%94%20and%20always%20aim%20to%20continuously%20expand%20your%20financial%20knowledge.%20%26quot%3BSmall%2C%20incremental%20changes%20can%20lead%20to%20significant%20success%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Truong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EConsider%20working%20with%20a%20professional%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChanges%20can%20be%20challenging%2C%20but%20that's%20how%20you'll%20grow.%20Get%20help%20from%20a%20professional.%20If%20you're%20wrestling%20with%20difficult%20emotions%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20guilt%20that%20you're%20failing%20your%20family%2C%20or%20a%20fear%20of%20losing%20them%20by%20setting%20boundaries%2C%20it%20could%20be%20helpful%20to%20work%20with%20a%20financial%20therapist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20help%20with%20your%20financial%20situation%20and%20juggling%20your%20needs%20and%20your%20family's%20needs%2C%20consider%20working%20with%20a%20financial%20advisor.%20Truong%20suggests%20looking%