%3Cspan%3E.%20Although%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20whether%20the%20disruption%20is%20intentional%2C%20Tallinn%20and%20Vilnius%20have%20accused%20Moscow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussia%20and%20Belarus%20have%20also%20been%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feu-seeks-ease-rules-poland-baltics-migration-standoff-with-belarus-2021-12-01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20accused%20by%20EU%20officials%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20pushing%20migrants%20towards%20the%20border%20of%20Lithuania%20and%20neighboring%20Poland%20and%20using%20them%20as%20hybrid%20weapons.%20Lithuania%20temporarily%20closed%20off%20some%20of%20its%20border%20crossings%20with%20Belarus%20in%20response%2C%20and%20Poland%20deployed%20troops%20to%20the%20border.%20The%20Baltics%20and%20Poland%20are%20prepared%20to%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fbelarus-border-wagner-migrants-poland-baltics-7f5d061f22785c433e436473b1d67937%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20close%20off%20their%20borders%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20major%20migrant%20push%20from%20Belarus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20three%20Baltic%20countries%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheweek.com%2Fdefence%2Fare-the-baltics-under-threat%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20influence%20operations%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Estonia%20has%20seen%20a%20rise%20in%20sabotages%20that%20included%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffinnish-police-complete-on-site-probe-damaged-baltic-sea-pipeline-2023-10-19%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20damage%20to%20an%20undersea%20gas%20pipeline%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20telecommunications%20cables%20between%20it%20and%20Finland.%20Espionage%2C%20cyber%20attacks%2C%20and%20election%20tampering%20are%20also%20a%20concern%2C%20with%20Estonia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Frussia-estonia-baltics-sabotage-spying-kallas-62835b00fdb31f648ebe2259908ca2a1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20having%20arrested%20the%20most%20Russian%20agents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20per%20capita%20in%20the%20EU.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2222b0c414-20e5-486c-9dcf-0082edb28b5b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EDestabilization%20is%20the%20point%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHybrid%20warfare%20can%20use%20various%20tools%20%E2%80%93%20including%20military%2C%20informational%2C%20economic%2C%20civilian%2C%20and%20others%20%E2%80%93%20but%20it%20falls%20short%20of%20overt%20military%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20purpose%20is%20to%20destabilize%20a%20country's%20government%2C%20institutions%2C%20or%20population%20while%20often%20preventing%20attribution%20back%20to%20the%20perpetrator%20%E2%80%93%20occasionally%2C%20a%20purposeful%20and%20targeted%20action%20may%20even%20appear%20to%20be%20a%20random%20event.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20speaks%20during%20the%20military%20parade%20at%20the%2076th%20Guards%20Air%20Assault%20Division%20in%20Pskov%2C%20Russia%2C%20March%2C1%2C2020.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66758564423319f0c3724f65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22661%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20speaks%20during%20the%20military%20parade%20at%20the%2076th%20Guards%20Air%20Assault%20Division%20in%20Pskov%2C%20Russia%2C%20March%201%2C%202020.%3Cp%3EMikhail%20Svetlov%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20hybrid%20warfare%20is%20not%20a%20new%20strategy%2C%20nor%20one%20employed%20exclusively%20by%20Russia%20and%20its%20al