0in%20my%20arms%20would%20become%20the%20teen%20driving%20a%20go-kart%20150%20miles%20away%20from%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20years%20following%20that%20first%20birthday%2C%20we%20threw%20many%20parties.%20From%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-bowling-alley-screen-memes-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebowling%20alley%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20karate%20dojo%20to%20a%20magician's%20stage%2C%20we%20celebrated%20my%20son%20on%20his%20special%20day%20because%20that's%20what%20you%20do%20when%20children%20turn%20another%20year%20older.%20Often%2C%20he'd%20awaken%20to%20a%20room%20filled%20with%20balloons.%20But%20sometimes%2C%20traditions%20change.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20mother%2C%20it%20was%20already%20hard%20to%20let%20go%20for%20the%20first%20time.%20I%20wanted%20him%20nearby%20so%20I%20could%20ensure%20he%20was%20happy%2C%20healthy%2C%20and%20safe.%20I%20worried%20he%20wouldn't%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-signs-youre-not-brushing-your-teeth-correctly-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebrush%20his%20teeth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20get%20sick%2C%20or%20like%20the%20food.%20Even%20worse%2C%20I%20was%20concerned%20he'd%20miss%20us%20during%20quiet%20nights%20as%20he%20lay%20awake%20in%20bed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a8aa5a0d-1d64-43f4-aaf7-11ff8cb26894%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son%20was%20ready%20for%20independence%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20packed%20his%20belongings%2C%20I%20remembered%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-hated-summer-camp-when-i-was-a-kid-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%20own%20summers%20at%20sleepover%20camp%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20I%20overwhelmingly%20recalled%20being%20homesick%20and%20wanting%20to%20go%20home.%20The%20day%20that%20stuck%20out%20most%20was%20my%2013th%20birthday%20when%20I%20snuck%20to%20the%20payphone%20to%20call%20my%20parents.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20come%20get%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20begged%2C%20even%20though%20I'd%20independently%20chosen%20to%20go%20back%20another%20summer.%20My%20own%20childhood%20emotions%20came%20rushing%20back%2C%20impeding%20me%20from%20sending%20my%20son%20off%20with%20ease.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20he%20was%20a%20different%20child%20altogether.%20He%20was%20ready.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-of-two-would-have-pay-8000-for-summer-camp-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eson%20heard%20about%20summer%20camp%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20the%20moment%20he%20could%20communicate.%20My%20husband%20went%20to%20the%20same%20camp%20himself%20and%20later%20worked%20there%20as%20a%20counselor.%20Stories%20of%20late-night%20firepits%2C%20hikes%20into%20the%20wilderness%2C%20and%20ziplining%20through%20the%20trees%20have%20been%20told%20in%20our%20home%20since%20my%20son%20could%20talk.%20My%20husband%20remains%20friends%20with%20some%20staff%20members%2C%20which%20gives%20my%20son%20a%20sense%20of%20community%20when%20he's%20away.%20Before%20he%20even%20arrived%20on%20day%20one%2C%20camp%20felt%20like%20a%20second%20home%20to%20him.%20No%20wonder%20he%20chooses%20to%20be%20away%20on%20his%20birthday%20each%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd8b33da-97c3-4e84-b6a6-7d1de40ed7e3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20saw%20photos%20of%20his%20birthday%20on%20an%20app%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20first%20summer%20away%2C%20I%20saw%20pictures%20from%20his%20birthday%20the%20following%20day%20on%20the%20Campanion%20app%20%E2%80%94%20the%20app%20where%20pictures%20of%20campers%20are%20uploaded%20daily.%20I%20waited%20anxiously%2C%20wanting%20to%20know%20if%20he'd