insider.com%2F6675c70265f501a881813c41%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUSS%20Constitution%20in%20the%20Boston%20Harbor%20in%20August%202019.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20Photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%203rd%20Class%20Casey%20Scoular%2FReleased%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUSS%20Constitution%20is%20the%20only%20remaining%20US%20Navy%20ship%20to%20have%20sunk%20an%20enemy%20warship%20in%20battle.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20is%20also%C2%A0the%20oldest%20commissioned%20warship%20in%20the%20world%20that's%20still%20afloat%2C%20and%20it's%20full%20of%20history.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20embarked%20on%20the%C2%A0226-year-old%20frigate%20for%20a%20recent%20underway%20in%20the%20Boston%20Harbor.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20sea%20shanties%20blaring%20on%20the%20loudspeaker%20and%20onlookers%20taking%20pictures%20from%20the%20shore%2C%20USS%20Constitution%20slowly%20pulled%20away%20from%20the%20pier%20on%20a%20blistering%20hot%20day%20in%20mid-June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20US%20Navy%20warship%2C%20at%20well%20over%20200%20years%20old%2C%20is%20not%20like%20the%20sea%20service's%20other%20ships%2C%20though.%20It%20is%20basically%20a%20floating%20museum%2C%20but%20with%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20twist.%20Unlike%20others%2C%20it%20hasn't%20been%20decommissioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution%2C%20known%20as%20America's%20Ship%20of%20State%2C%20needed%20a%20tugboat's%20assistance%20for%20the%20entirety%20of%20an%20hours-long%20underway%20in%20the%20Boston%20Harbor%20to%20honor%20women%20veterans%20of%20the%20US%20armed%20forces.%20When%20it%20sets%20sail%2C%20the%20tall%20ship%20moves%20slowly%2C%20escorted%20by%20police%20boats%20and%20the%20Coast%20Guard%20and%20helicopters%20circling%20overhead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAboard%20are%20hundreds%20of%20people%20%E2%80%94%20veterans%2C%20active-duty%20personnel%2C%20and%20their%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20warship%20sailed%20the%20harbor%