s%20love%20bagels.%20I'm%20convinced%20it's%20the%20New%20Yorker%20in%20them%2C%20and%20Costco%20allows%20them%20to%20get%20their%20fix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20have%20different%20tastes%20and%20preferences%2C%20so%20Costco's%20two-for-%247%20deal%20on%20Kirkland%20Signature%20bagels%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20ensure%20they%20each%20have%20what%20they%20like.%20I%20usually%20pick%20up%20everything%20and%20plain%20for%20the%20kids%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20I'll%20grab%20a%20cinnamon-raisin%20pack%20for%20myself.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESimply%20Orange%20pulp-free%20orange%20juice%20gets%20a%20thumbs%20up%20from%20my%20daughter.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223645%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Packages%20of%20Simpley%20Orange%20juice%20on%20shelf%20at%20Costco.%20Each%2012-pack%20has%20bottles%20filled%20with%20a%20yellow-orange%20juice%20and%20green%20caps%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664b76ba20abc1efe8fb911d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222734%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20daughter%20is%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20the%20Simply%20Orange%20pulp-free%20orange%20juice.%3Cp%3ELeslie%20Antonoff%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20big%20fans%20of%20the%20Simply%20juices.%20I%20usually%20opt%20for%20either%20the%20brand's%20Simply%20Lemonade%2C%20Simply%20Limeade%2C%20or%20Simply%20Peach%20flavors%2C%20but%20at%20Costco%2C%20we%20get%20the%20Simply%20Orange%20juice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I'm%20not%20a%20huge%20orange-juice%20drinker%2C%20my%20teenager%20loves%20to%20take%20a%20small%20bottle%20with%20her%20to%20school.%20A%20case%20of%20Simply%20Orange%20juice%20is%20%2416%20at%20my%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EServing%20pasta%20once%20a%20week%20means%20there%20has%20to%20be%20cheese%20available.%C2%A0%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20hand%20holds%20a%20large%20piece%20of%20Kirkland%20Signature%20Parmesan%20cheese%20with%20a%20black%20label%20and%20