ling%20two%20cars%2C%20their%20furniture%2C%20and%20other%20possessions%2C%20they%20converted%20a%20cargo%20van%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-lives-in-tiny-home-on-wheels-with-office-bedroom-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etiny%20home%20on%20wheels%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20spent%20three%20years%20traveling.%20They%20wintered%20in%20warmer%20states%20like%20Florida%20and%20California%20and%20spent%20summers%20exploring%20the%20serene%20nature%20of%20British%20Columbia%20and%20Alberta%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpectation-vs-reality-van-life-trip-not-like-social-media-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVan%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20filled%20with%20%26quot%3Bendless%20possibilities%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20Bidlens%20knew%20it%20wouldn't%20last%20forever.%20Becky%2C%20a%20travel%20nurse%2C%20and%20Drew%2C%20who%20works%20in%20software%2C%20eventually%20wanted%20to%20settle%20down%20and%20have%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-makes-six-figures-freelancing-remotely-side-hustle-van-life2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20millennials%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20generation%20drawn%20to%20the%20adventurous%20spirit%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-couple-shares-tips-living-debt-free-rv-tiny-home-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erelative%20affordability%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20van%20life%2C%20they%20saved%20thousands%20by%20working%20remotely%2C%20living%20frugally%2C%20and%2C%20importantly%2C%20not%20spending%20a%20dime%20on%20rent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20the%20couple%20welcomed%20their%20daughter%2C%20Aurora%20Mercy.%20Twelve%20days%20later%2C%20they%20found%20what%20they%20were%20looking%20for%3A%20a%20historic%20house%20in%20Indianapolis%2C%20close%20to%20where%20most%20of%20Becky's%20family%20still%20l