ut%20it%2C%20seeing%20the%20potential%20and%20seeing%20the%20price%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Becky%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20took%20on%20something%20a%20bit%20bigger%20than%20we%20had%20anticipated%2C%20but%20still%20felt%20like%20it%20was%20something%20we%20could%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20its%20size%20and%20price%2C%20Becky%20and%20Drew%20weren't%20the%20only%20ones%20keen%20on%20the%20house.%20To%20show%20they%20were%20serious%2C%20they%20made%20a%20higher%20offer%20of%20%24150%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20the%20day%20they%20closed%20on%20the%20house%2C%20Becky%20said%20she%20initially%20felt%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20sick%26quot%3B%20about%20their%20choice.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20stacked%20bookshelf%20in%20the%20background%20of%20a%20room%20covered%20in%20furniture%2C%20books%2C%20and%20other%20items.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671adef087acd2be9b4914a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20former%20owner%20collected%20books%2C%20coins%2C%20crystals%2C%20and%20stamps.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Drew%20and%20Becky%20Bidlen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20she's%20a%20%26quot%3Bdreamer%26quot%3B%20who%20has%20seen%20some%20%26quot%3Bugly%20stuff%26quot%3B%20in%20previous%20homes%2C%20Becky%20couldn't%20help%20feeling%20some%20trepidation%20about%20how%20much%20work%20they%20were%20in%20for%20with%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20closing%20day%2C%20she%20said%20she%20felt%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20sick%26quot%3B%20thinking%20about%20whether%20they%20made%20the%20right%20choice.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20'What%20did%20we%20just%20buy%3F%20We%20don't%20even%20know%20what's%20under%20all%20this%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Becky%2C%20there%20were%20piles%20of%20stuff%20in%20every%20room%2C%20filled%20with%20everything%20from%20trash%20and%20furniture%20to%20gadgets%20and%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20just%20all%20mixed%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20would%20have%20a%20box%20with%20some%20sweaters%20and%20then%20Inuit-carved%20arts%20and%20china.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20didn't%20want%20to%20pay%20roughly%20%2410%2C000%20for%20someone%20to%20sort%20and%20clear%20all%20of%20the%20items%2C%20so%20Becky%20and%20Drew%20enlisted%20the%20help%20of%20family%20and%20friends.%20The%20weekslong%20process%20became%20somewhat%20of%20a%20treasure%20hunt%2C%20as%20the%20couple%20told%20their%20volunteers%20that%20if%20they%20found%20something%20they%20wanted%2C%20they%20could%20probably%20keep%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mom%20took%20a%20Waterpik%20flosser%20that%20was%20new%2C%20and%20she%20was%20really%20excited%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Becky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBeneath%20the%20layers%20of%20trash%2C%20dirt%2C%20and%20a%20few%20found%20treasures%20was%20a%20real%20issue%3A%20mold.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bathroom%20covered%20in%20mold%20and%20dirt.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671ad39a76074d191cce1d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20house%20was%20full%20of%20mold%20when%20the%20Bidlens%20bought%20it.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Drew%20and%20Becky%20Bidlen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20couple%20cleared%20out%20all%20the%20unsalvageable%20items%2C%20they%20were%20left%20with%20a%20few%20things%20of%20value%2C%20including%20jewelry%20and%20collections%20of%20coins%2C%20stamps%2C%20and%20crystals.%20They%20plan%20to%20get%20them%20appraised%20and%20decide%20whether%20to%20sell%2C%20donate%2C%20or%20keep%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20more%20urgent%20problem%3A%20The%20building%20wasn't%20properly%20%26quot%3Bwinterized%26quot%3B%20and%20sustained%20significant%20water%20damage%2C%20leading%20to%20mold%20on%20the%20first%20and%20second%20floors%2C%20Becky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20mold%20remediation%20process%20has%20been%20a%20whole%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Becky%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they've%20done%20most%20of%20it%20themselves%20after%20consulting%20a%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20mold%20is%20the%20reason%20they're%20still%20waiting%20to%20move%20into%20the%20property%2C%20which%20they%20hope%20to%20finally%20do%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20related%20to%20the%20air%20quality%20has%20been%20extremely%20tedious%2C%20especially%20with%20the%20mold%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20couple%20quickly%20discovered%20that%20their%20house%20had%20also%20been%20overrun%20with%20raccoons%2C%20who%20left%20%26quot%3Bankle-deep%26quot%3B%20droppings%20in%20the%20attic.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20house%20with%20holes%20in%20the%20ceiling%20and%20dirt%20gathering%20across%20the%20floors.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671ad83087acd2be9b490f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFamilies%20of%20raccoons%20burrowed%20holes%20into%20the%20attic.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Drew%20and%20Becky%20Bidlen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20a%20raccoon%20infestation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20primary%20resident%20in%20our%20attic%20was%20raccoons%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20even%20know%20how%20much%20were%20in%20there%2C%20but%20they%20left%20a%20lot%20of%20droppings%2C%20like%20ankle-deep.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20critters%20also%20left%20their%20mark%20by%20burrowing%20gaping%20holes%20in%20the%20floors%20and%20ceilings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Bidlens%20had%20renovated%20the%20van%20they%20lived%20out%20of%2C%20so%20they%20felt%20prepared%20to%20take%20on%20a%20bigger%20project.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Drew%20and%20Becky%20Bidlen%20in%20their%20van%20(Left)%20and%20a%20wide%20shot%20of%20the%20van's%20interior.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6671ae9b2efa138e0330a4bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bidlens%20in%20their%20van%20after%20renovating%20it%20themselves.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Drew%20and%20Becky%20Bidlen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERenovating%20a%20house%20is%20a%20much%20bigger%20project%20than%20fixing%20up%20a%20vehicle%2C%20but%20Becky%20said%20turning%20their%20van%20into%20a%20home%20years%20before%20served%20as%20great%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20our%20first%20introduction%20to%20working%20on%20projects%20together%2C%20and%20it%20was%20quite%20challenging%2C%20but%20it%20was%20good%20to%20learn%20plumbing%2C%20electrical%2C%20woodworking%2C%20flooring%2C%20and%20insulation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast-forward%20to%202024%2C%20and%20Becky%20said%20they've%20made%20almost%20all%20the%20major%20changes%20they%20want%20to%20the%20hoarder%20home.%20They%20replaced%20all%20the%20plumbing%20and%20adjusted%20a%20wall%20and%20beams%20between%20the%20kitchen%20and%20the%20sunroom%20to%20make%20the%20cooking%20area%20brighter%20and%20warmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20salvaging%20the%20hardwood%20floors%2C%20some%20of%20which%20have%20been%20damaged%20by%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20finding%20an%20old%20fire%20map%20of%20the%20home%2C%20Becky%20said%20they%20discovered%20it%20once%20had%20a%20wraparound%20porch%2C%20a%20feature%20they%20intend%20to%20restore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20keep%20as%20much%20of%20the%20historic%20charm%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Becky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20couple's%20passion%20for%20preservation%20is%20inspired%20by%20their%20time%20living%