3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c9935ed9a404d829e0eaa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMissed%20opp%3A%20bringing%20the%20cat.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226ba4148d-bff9-4aa7-b531-18e6c937db3b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKeep%20the%20heavier%20items%20towards%20the%20top%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECihlar%20said%20that%20your%20shoulders%20sometimes%20feel%20sore%20when%20you%20start%20rucking.%20While%20that%20was%20definitely%20true%20for%20me%20the%20first%20times%20I%20walked%20to%20work%2C%20I'd%20also%20feel%20that%20lower%20back%20ache%2C%20sometimes%20for%20days%20afterward.%20It%20made%20me%20more%20cautious%20about%20adding%20more%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20not%20using%20an%20actual%20ruck%2C%20which%20holds%20the%20weight%20up%20high%20on%20your%20back%2C%20and%20you're%20just%20loading%20your%20backpack%2C%20everything%20falls%20to%20the%20bottom%2C%26quot%3B%20Cihlar%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20can%20cause%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20weight%20tension%20sitting%20in%20your%20low%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20packing%20my%20bag%2C%20I%20rearranged%20its%20contents%20and%20piled%20heavier%20items%2C%20like%20my%20lunch%20and%20my%20makeup%20bag%2C%20closer%20to%20the%20top.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20backpack%20with%20a%20Tupperware%20of%20lunch%20and%20a%20cosmetics%20bag%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F666c9996764df161125a20bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223991%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELunch%2C%20a%20makeup%20bag%2C%20and%20bug%20spray%20were%20a%20few%20of%20the%20things%20I%20stacked%20on%20top.%3Cp%3EJulia%20Pugachevsky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20a%20huge%20difference%20during%20the%20walk.%20My%20shoulders%20were%20a%20lot%20more%20sore%20than%20in%20the%20past%2C%20while%20my%20back