0need%20to%20treat%20everyone%20equally%20rather%20than%20focus%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20individual%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20team%20sport%2C%20it's%20the%20team%20that%20matters%20the%20most.%20It's%20the%20team%20that%20is%20the%20most%20important%20ingredient%20in%20that%20organisation.%20Individuals%20do%20play%20a%20role%2C%20and%20individuals%20do%20contribute%2C%20but%20ultimately%2C%20if%2011%20people%20are%20treated%20equally%2C%20if%2011%20people%20have%20equal%20respect%2C%20if%20everyone%20is%20treated%20equally%2C%20given%20the%20same%20respect%2C%20same%20responsibility%2C%20given%20the%20same%20honour%2C%20you%20will%20achieve%20an%20unbelievable%20amount%20of%20success.%20You%20cannot%20have%20discrimination%20in%20a%20set-up%20or%20in%20an%20organisation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20is%20currently%20thriving%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20after%20they%20began%20their%20Super%208%20campaign%20with%20a%2047-run%20win%20over%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20unbeaten%20side%20will%20face%20Bangladesh%20on%20Saturday%20at%20Sir%20Vivian%20Richards%20Stadium%20in%20Antigua.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719052140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Ff7h3h71o_gautam-gambhir-bcci_625x300_26_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgrilling-me-gautam-gambhir-blunt-response-on-india-coach-appointment-talks-5942943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20cricketer%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20addressed%20his%20future%20as%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20men's%20national%20team%20and%20stated%20that%20he%20isn't%20%26quot%3Blooking%20far%20ahead%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20is%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20space%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20moment.%22%2C%22author%22%3