es.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnight-watchman-found-dead-in-paris-hotel-after-robbery-bid%2Farticleshow%2F111187674.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnight-watchman-found-dead-in-paris-hotel-after-robbery-bid%2Famp_articleshow%2F111187674.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fnight-watchman-found-dead-in-paris-hotel-after-robbery-bid%2Famp_articleshow%2F111187674.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Are%20The%20Hindujas%20-%20Billionaires%20Facing%20Jail%20Term%20For%20Exploiting%20Staff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%201914.%20A%20young%20entrepreneur%20from%20the%20Shikarpur%20town%20of%20Sindh%20district%2C%20then%20part%20of%20undivided%20India%2C%20had%20travelled%20to%20Bombay%20(now%20Mumbai).%20His%20name%20was%20Parmanand%20Deepchand%20Hinduja%2C%20and%20he%20founded%20what%20would%2C%20over%20the%20next%20100%20years%2C%20become%20an%20enviable%20global%20business%20empire%20worth%20%2420%20billion.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hinduja%20Group%20expanded%20to%20shipping%2C%20banking%2C%20media%2C%20and%20real%20estate%2C%20including%20London's%20prestigious%20Raffles%20Hotel%2C%20eventually%20making%20them%20the%20richest%20family%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20Hinduja%20empire%20is%20managed%20by%20four%20brothers%20%E2%80%93%20Srichand%2C%20Gopichand%2C%20Prakash%20and%20Ashok.%20Srichand%20and%20Gopichand%20are%20based%20in%20London%20and%20focus%20on%20the%20group's%20interests%20in%20Europe%20and%20America.%20Prakash%20oversees%20European%20operations%20from%20Geneva%20while%20Ashok%20manages%20the%20group's%20India%20ventures%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20particularly%20in%20media%20and%20communications.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20contribute%20to%20healthcare%2C%20education%2C%20and%20rural%20development%20through%20the%20Hinduja%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20philanthropic%20contributions%2C%20recent%20legal%20issues%20have%20overshadowed%20the%20Hindujas'%20legacy.%20Four%20members%20of%20the%20Hinduja%20family%20were%20sentenced%20to%20prison%20by%20a%20Swiss%20court%20on%20Friday%20for%20exploiting%20their%20household%20staff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20trial%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fuks-hinduja-family-prakash-hinduja-ajay-hinduja-geneva-billionaire-hinduja-family-accused-of-exploiting-staff-at-swiss-villa-report-5915321%C2%A0%5C%22%3EThe%20trial%20in%20Geneva%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20disturbing%20details%20of%20mistreatment%20at%20the%20Hinduja%20family's%20Swiss%20villa.%20They%20were%20accused%20of%20underpaying%20workers%20and%20keeping%20them%20on%20call%20without%20proper%20breaks.%20Prosecutors%20also%20alleged%20that%20while%20the%20family%20spent%20lavishly%20on%20their%20pet%20dog%2C%20some%20staff%20members%20earned%20as%20little%20as%20Rs%20600%20a%20day%20for%2018%20hours%20of%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20also%20reportedly%20confiscated%20their%20staff's%20passports%2C%20restricting%20their%20freedom%20to%20leave%20the%20premises%20without%20permission%2C%20attracting%20human%20trafficking%20charges%20under%20Swiss%20law.%20Staff%20members%20were%20paid%20in%20Indian%20currency%2C%20leaving%20them%20without%20money%20in%20Switzerland.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20also%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cclimate%20of%20fear%E2%80%9D%20around%20the%20house%20and%20they%20had%20to%20work%20without%20breaks%20and%20were%20made%20to%20sleep%20on%20mattresses%20in%20the%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20are%20the%20ones%20sentenced%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakash%20Hinduja%20and%20his%20wife%20Kamal%20Hinduja%20have%20been%20sentenced%20to%20four%20years%20and%20six%20months%20in%20prison.%20His%20son%20Ajay%2C%2056%2C%20and%20his%20wife%20Namrata%2C%2050%2C%20were%20sentenced%20to%20four%20years%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakash%20P%20Hinduja%2C%2078%2C%20is%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Hinduja%20Group%20of%20Companies%20(Europe)%20and%20Advisory%20Board%20Chairman%20at%20Hinduja%20Bank%20Switzerland.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20Board%20member%20of%20the%20Swiss%20Indian%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20the%20family%20business%20in%20Tehran%2C%20Iran%2C%20after%20completing%20his%20University%20education%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakash%20and%20Kamal%20Hinduja%2C%2075%2C%20have%20another%20son%2C%20Ramkrishan%2C%20and%20a%20daughter%20named%20Renuka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719049380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fuk20otj_hindujas-afp_625x300_22_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-are-the-hindujas-billionaires-facing-jail-term-for-exploiting-staff-5943857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prakash%20Hinduja%20and%20his%20wife%20Kamal%2C%20each%20received%20four%20years%20and%20six%20months%20while%20their%20son%20Ajay%20and%20his%20wife%20Namrata%20were%20sentenced%20to%20four%20years%20each%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Geneva%20judge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-are-the-hindujas-billionaires-facing-jail-term-for-exploiting-staff-5943857%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-are-the-hindujas-billionaires-facing-jail-term-for-exploiting-staff-5943857%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwho-are-the-hindujas-billionaires-facing-jail-term-for-exploiting-s