ver-video-viral-5944946%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-haryana-traffic-cop-dragged-by-drunk-driver-video-viral-5944946%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fon-camera-haryana-traffic-cop-dragged-by-drunk-driver-video-viral-5944946%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gambhir%20Urges%20ICC%20To%20Revisit%20This%20Rule%2C%20Says%20'Unfair'%20For%20Finger%20Spinners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20opener%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20on%20Friday%20urged%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20to%20revisit%20the%20two%20new-ball%20rule%20in%20limited%20over%20formats%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Cup-winner%20termed%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20to%20finger%20spinners.%20The%20ICC%20had%20implemented%20the%20particular%20rule%20in%20ODIs%20in%20October%202011%2C%20something%20the%20legendary%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20had%20rated%20as%20%26quot%3Bperfect%20recipe%20for%20disaster.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOne%20thing%20I%20would%20definitely%20change%20is%20the%20use%20of%20two%20new%20balls%2C%20especially%20in%20white-ball%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Gambhir%20said%20during%20the%20'Rise%20to%20Leadership'%20talk%20show%20by%20the%20Indian%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce.%20The%20stipulation%20to%20use%20two%20new%20balls%2C%20several%20experts%20felt%2C%20has%20disadvantaged%20finger%20spinners%20and%20reduced%20the%20chances%20of%20reverse%20swing%20as%20it%20helps%20the%20ball%20to%20retain%20the%20shine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unfair%20for%20finger%20spinners%2C%20who%20are%20not%20playing%20enough%20white-ball%20cricket%20because%20there%20is%20nothing%20for%20them.%20It%20is%20not%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC's%20job%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20everyone%2C%20whether%20a%20finger%20spinner%2C%20fast%20bowler%2C%20wrist%20spinner%2C%20or%20batter%2C%20has%20an%20equal%20opportunity%20to%20showcase%20their%20talents%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gambhir%2C%20who%20recently%20mentored%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20during%20their%20run%20to%20the%20third%20IPL%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20is%20also%20viewed%20as%20the%20frontrunner%20to%20become%20next%20India%20coach%20following%20Rahul%20Dravid's%20exit%20after%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-time%20IPL%20winning%20former%20skipper%20asked%20the%20ICC%20to%20have%20a%20review%20of%20the%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTaking%20that%20opportunity%20away%20from%20certain%20players%20is%20very%20unfair.%20Today%2C%20you%20hardly%20see%20any%20finger%20spinners%20playing%20white-ball%20cricket.%20Why%3F%20The%20blame%20lies%20not%20with%20them%2C%20but%20with%20the%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20reverse%20swing%20anymore%20because%20of%20the%20two%20new%20balls%2C%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20for%20finger%20spinners%20or%20left-arm%20spinners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20I%20would%20want%20to%20change%2C%20and%20hopefully%2C%20it%20will%20change%20to%20create%20a%20balance%20between%20bat%20and%20ball%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Gambhir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%2C%20who%20played%20under%20various%20captains%2C%20refrained%20from%20naming%20the%20best%20skipper%2C%20but%20hailed%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20said%20the%20best%20phase%20of%20his%20career%20was%20under%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20such%20a%20controversial%20question.%20I%20honestly%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20headlines%2C%20everyone%20had%20their%20strength%20and%20weaknesses.%20I%20made%20my%20Test%20debut%20under%20Rahul%20Dravid%20and%20ODI%20under%20(Sourav)%20Ganguly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20my%20best%20performance%20under%20Anil%20Kumble%20and%20I%20had%20my%20phase%20under%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20and%20the%20longest%20I%20played%20was%20under%20MS.%20I%20enjoyed%20playing%20a%20lot%20with%20MS%20and%20the%20way%20he%20led%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20also%20hailed%20Bollywood%20star%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20as%20the%20best%20team%20owner%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20working%20with%20the%20best%20IPL%20owner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719047220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcmu29hro_gautam-gambhir_625x300_20_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-urges-icc-to-revisit-this-rule-says-unfair-for-finger-spinners-5941320%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20urged%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20to%20revisit%20the%20two%20new-ball%20rule%20in%20limited%20over%20formats%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Cup-winner%20termed%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Bunfair%26quot%3B%20to%20finger%20spinners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-urges-icc-to-revisit-this-rule-says-unfair-for-finger-spinners-5941320%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-urges-icc-to-revisit-this-rule-says-unfair-for-finger-spinners-5941320%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-urges-icc-to-revisit-this-rule-says-unfair-for-finger-spinners-5941320%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Clash%20of%20thieves%3A%20Two%20thugs%20race%2C%20fight%20with%20each%20other%20to%20steal%20package%20in%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719046814000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111187044%2Cimgsize-2840636.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-thieves-fight-to-steal-fedx-package-video-caught-on-camera%2Farticleshow%2F111185770.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%