0other%20high-calibre%20weapons%20from%20a%20Pakistani%20arms%20dealer.%20The%20plan%20was%20to%20either%20ambush%20the%20star's%20car%20or%20attack%20his%20farmhouse%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20men%20have%20been%20arrested%20after%20two%20men%20on%20a%20bike%20opened%20fire%20outside%20Salman%20Khan's%20home%20on%20April%2014.%20Vicky%20Gupta%20and%20Sagar%20Pal%20were%20arrested%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20while%20Anuj%20Thapan%20and%20another%20man%20were%20detained%20in%20Punjab%20on%20April%2026.%20Anuj%20Thapan%20died%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719043020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fpp45f7go_salman-khan_625x300_08_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreakthrough-in-salman-khan-firing-case-audio-of-gangsters-call-to-shooter-5944615%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20police%20have%20recovered%20an%20audio%20file%20which%20establishes%20a%20link%20between%20the%20Lawrence%20Bishnoi%20gang%20and%20the%20attackers%20who%20shot%20at%20actor%20Salman%20Khan's%20house%20in%20April.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreakthrough-in-salman-khan-firing-case-audio-of-gangsters-call-to-shooter-5944615%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreakthrough-in-salman-khan-firing-case-audio-of-gangsters-call-to-shooter-5944615%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbreakthrough-in-salman-khan-firing-case-audio-of-gangsters-call-to-shooter-5944615%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2239%20yrs%20on%2C%20Canada's%20probe%20into%20AI%20bombing%20still%20'active%2C%20ongoing'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719042459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111186050%2Cimgsize-1583631.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesof