ausing%20one%20of%20them%20to%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20has%20completely%20cut%20off%20access%20across%20the%20Gandak%20canal%2C%20forcing%20residents%20to%20travel%20long%20distances%20to%20reach%20neighbouring%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20just%20days%20after%20a%20similar%20incident%20in%20Araria%2C%20where%20a%20concrete%20bridge%20over%20the%20Bakra%20River%2C%20built%20after%20spending%20crores%2C%20came%20apart%20in%20seconds.%20Visuals%20showed%20the%20bridge%2C%20over%20the%20fast-flowing%20river%2C%20tilted%20on%20one%20side%20and%20a%20crowd%20gathered%20on%20the%20banks%20near%20the%20bridge%2C%20recording%20the%20moment%20it%20collapsed.%20Built%20at%20Rs%2012%20crore%2C%20the%20bridge%20collapsed%20before%20its%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719040740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Flscdqf3s_bihar-bridge-collapse_625x300_22_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbridge-collapse-in-siwan-creates-panic-2nd-incident-in-bihar-this-week-5944398%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sudden%20collapse%20of%20a%20bridge%20in%20Bihar's%20Siwan%20today%20caused%20widespread%20panic%20and%20uproar%20in%20the%20area.%20The%20collapse%20of%20the%20bridge%20over%20the%20Gandak%20canal%20occurred%20with%20a%20loud%20noise%20that%20was%20heard%20till%20the%20neighbouring%20Ramgarh%20in%20Darbhanga%20district.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbridge-collapse-in-siwan-creates-panic-2nd-incident-in-bihar-this-week-5944398%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbridge-collapse-in-siwan-creates-panic-2nd-incident-in-bihar-this-week-5944398%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbridge-collapse-in-siwan-creates-panic-2nd-incident-in-bihar-this-week-594439