s%20failure%20as%20part%20of%20the%20journey%20and%20did%20not%20feel%20discouraged.%20Also%2C%20there%20was%20only%20a%20marginal%20gap%20in%20marks%2C%20so%20I%20could%20try%20one%20more%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20he%20failed%20in%20prelims%20in%20the%20fourth%20attempt.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20a%20major%20setback%20for%20me.%20I%20was%20disheartened.%20But%20I%20understood%20that%20something%20was%20lacking%20in%20my%20strategy%20because%20of%20which%20I%20was%20either%20failing%20prelims%20or%20Mains%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20did%20wonder%20if%20he%20should%20quit%20preparation%20and%20go%20back%20to%20corporate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20Ashish%20was%20motivated%20to%20give%20one%20last%20try.%20He%20appeared%20for%20his%20fifth%20attempt%20and%20finally%20achieved%20success%20%E2%80%94%20securing%20an%20impressive%20AIR%208!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFive%20ultimate%20tips%20to%20guarantee%20success%20in%20UPSC%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20shares%20how%20he%20changed%20his%20strategy%20in%20the%20fifth%20attempt%20to%20clear%20UPSC%20CSE%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Be%20Consistent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20the%20fifth%20attempt%2C%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20needed%20to%20study%2C%20but%20I%20lacked%20consistency.%20If%20you%20have%20decided%20to%20become%20a%20civil%20servant%2C%20you%20must%20work%20hard%20consistently.%20So%2C%20if%20you%20study%20for%20four%20days%20and%20then%20rest%20for%20the%20next%20four%20days%2C%20then%20you%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20achieve%20success.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20study%20all%20eight%20days%20even%20though%20for%20fewer%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20How%20to%20read%20the%20newspaper%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshish%20says%20his%20day%20started%20by%20reading%20the%20newspaper%20%E2%80%94%20either%20The%20Hindu%20or%20The%20In